</s>
<s id="celex_31985L0203-s4">
  <english>This Directive shall not apply to exposure at work or inside buildings .</english>
  <czech>Tato směrnice se nevztahuje na expozici oxidu dusičitému v pracovním prostředí nebo uvnitř budov .</czech>
  <sure>1-1 2-2 4-4 5-4 6-5 7-6 8-9 9-10 9-11 10-12 11-13 12-14 13-15</sure>
